initialize:
=== Parameters
+SSLSocket+ is an OpenSSL::SSL::SSLSocket
+string+ must be a DER or PEM encoded Session.
time: Gets start time of the session.
time=: Sets start time of the session. Time resolution is in seconds.
timeout: Gets how long until the session expires in seconds.
timeout=: Sets how long until the session expires in seconds.
to_der: Returns an ASN1 encoded String that contains the Session object.
to_pem: Returns a PEM encoded String that contains the Session object.
to_text: Shows everything in the Session object.
